Brazillian method of make caramell.
 Ingredients:
   1) Amount of sugar var of the amount of sauce.
      This Example: 2 Cups of sugar
   2) 1/5 Spoon of unsalted butter
   3) 1/2 cup of milk
   
 Instructions:
   1) Sugar in the bowl, put low fire and mixture all
      alert to don't ultrapass the time
   2) then after passed to liquid you put the butter inside and keep mixing until make one homogen form
   3) then keep alert to the vapor that exit of bowl and put the cup of milk in the bowl
   5) keep mixing until the solid form turn into liquid form again then the recipe it's finished.

go fast the liquid after enter in contact with lower temperatures solidify again
